over the county line again, don't call me.

27:07.687 --> 27:10.918
Now, if you'll just sign this here now,
get it over with...

27:11.607 --> 27:13.040
Here, sign it.

27:26.447 --> 27:28.358
Out. Now.

28:33.247 --> 28:35.397
You don't have to go home, Bertha.

28:36.327 --> 28:39.364
We can put you and the kid up
in a motel tonight.

28:39.887 --> 28:42.276
Tomorrow, you and I...

28:44.687 --> 28:46.325
can talk things out.

29:02.127 --> 29:03.355
Bertha.

29:04.407 --> 29:05.362
Bertha...

29:05.767 --> 29:07.564
there's nothing to go home to.

29:13.207 --> 29:15.163
I went to high school with her.

29:23.847 --> 29:25.439
She was the first.

29:30.927 --> 29:35.079
AMOS: Thas it. Bertha, get in that truck,
