29:39.727 --> 29:42.685
- Whiskey! Les go to the club.
- All right, I'm buying.

29:42.767 --> 29:45.725
You said a good thing there.
Or was that me?

29:46.607 --> 29:49.167
You know what your father once said to me?

29:52.487 --> 29:55.126
I was gonna make it up anyhow.
How you doing?

29:55.247 --> 29:56.839
You know, this morning all I had to do...

29:56.927 --> 30:00.158
was to figure out some way
to get the girls to accept Lauren.

30:02.367 --> 30:03.436
Yeah.

30:07.007 --> 30:10.283
Are you gonna stand there philosophising,
or are you gonna buy me a drink?

30:10.367 --> 30:13.643
You're not smart enough to do both.
Now, come on. Come on, boy.

30:14.087 --> 30:16.282
Whatever happened to last Thursday?

30:16.367 --> 30:20.485
I had it made last Thursday.
Ev, what the hell's going on around here?

30:20.847 --> 30:23.077
Wade. Come here.

30:24.727 --> 30:27.082
AMOS: Get in the truck! Just like I told you...

30:27.967 --> 30:29.639
and sit down under that steering wheel.

30:29.727 --> 30:31.638
Now look at that.
Doesn't that turn your stomach?

30:31.727 --> 30:32.682
AMOS: For Goďs sake!

30:32.767 --> 30:34.803
EVERETT: Be a liar, be a cheat...

30:35.287 --> 30:37.642
be antisocial, all of which he is.

30:38.727 --> 30:41.799
But don't be a bully. I hate bullies.

30:43.247 --> 30:44.965
Now, come on, les have a drink.

30:45.047 --> 30:47.800
Order me a gin and tonic. I'll wait for Luke.

30:48.167 --> 30:50.283
