32:04.487 --> 32:06.079
I'll blow the son of a bitch sky high.

32:06.167 --> 32:07.077
Don't push me, pig face.

32:07.167 --> 32:09.727
Twenty-two gun-toting idiots,
and you guys can't bag...

32:09.807 --> 32:11.286
some pretty little jackass out for kicks.

32:11.367 --> 32:13.039
- All I want of you...
- You let me out of here.

32:13.127 --> 32:15.083
- Shut up!
- I'll put you two...

32:15.167 --> 32:18.796
All I want from you is to know if is
the same car that killed the hitchhiker.

32:19.807 --> 32:22.765
- Yeah.
- Tell me slowly...

32:23.887 --> 32:26.879
so I can understand what happened.

32:29.207 --> 32:31.402
I was crossing the street to go to the club...

32:31.487 --> 32:34.843
he came out of the dark,
he looked like he was heading right at me...

32:34.927 --> 32:37.964
he swerved, I dove, he hit Everett...

32:38.047 --> 32:40.845
it was the same guy, and thas all I know.

32:48.287 --> 32:50.437
What did you get from her? Anything?

32:50.527 --> 32:53.963
- She says it was a black car.
- Well, doesn't she know what kind?

32:54.647 --> 32:56.603
[Speaking in Navajo]

33:00.527 --> 33:01.676
Big and black.

33:01.767 --> 33:05.077
I called Daigler County.
They're watching, but no sign of him.

33:05.167 --> 33:08.204
Well, he had to crawl into Daigler County?
He had to cross the county line.

33:08.287 --> 33:10.926
There's only one road out of here.
There's no other way.

33:11.007 --> 33:13.726
- I told them.
- Okay, what happened?

33:16.407 --> 33:19.558
[Speaking in Navajo]

33:26.967 --> 33:29.356
He swerved around Clements
and then hit Ev.

33:38.247 --> 33:39.805
What did she say?

33:41.207 --> 33:44.802
She's an old woman.
Indian talk, it doesn't matter.

33:44.887 --> 33:46.605
What did she say, Chas?

33:49.527 --> 33:52.883
Moccasin telegraph says
bad things are coming with the wind.

33:52.967 --> 33:55.242
Her family's going deeper
into back country tomorrow.

33:56.727 --> 33:57.762
What do you think?

33:59.447 --> 34:00.436
About what?

34:01.327 --> 34:03.363
Well, what do you want to do?

34:09.927 --> 34:11.679
How the hell do I know?

34:33.967 --> 34:37.357
Well, thas it, guys.
It looked like he went over the hills.

34:37.527 --> 34:39.563
But we'll keep everything going.

34:39.806 --> 34:42.446
Roadblocks and so forth,
