34:48.206 --> 34:50.801
I wanna thank you all for hanging in there.

34:51.487 --> 34:53.955
What can I tell you? Go to it.

34:57.847 --> 34:58.916
DONNA: Okay.

35:00.567 --> 35:01.682
Thas good.

