36:16.167 --> 36:18.397
- I can do it.
- Right here.

36:18.647 --> 36:22.196
I had nobody else to ask, you know,
about the funeral arrangements.

36:22.487 --> 36:24.398
Give us a couple of days.

36:24.727 --> 36:25.682
He was a...

36:26.727 --> 36:28.763
- He was a Methodist.
- Thas right.

36:29.647 --> 36:32.366
The guys and I'll chip in for the expenses.

36:32.447 --> 36:34.165
There won't be any charge.

36:34.407 --> 36:37.797
Okay, I guess I've got all I need. Thank you.

36:38.847 --> 36:40.519
At least thas one of us.

36:40.647 --> 36:41.966
Wade...

36:42.647 --> 36:45.684
there's something I wanna tell you
about last night.

36:46.407 --> 36:48.125
Well, the old lady.

36:48.207 --> 36:51.836
Well, Chas, he didn't translate
everything that she said.

36:52.287 --> 36:54.278
- What do you mean?
- Well...

36:54.847 --> 36:56.166
she said...

36:56.887 --> 36:59.117
there was no driver in the car.

37:07.607 --> 37:09.086
Thanks, Donna.

37:15.687 --> 37:18.201
Thomas County Sheriff, may I help you?

37:24.607 --> 37:25.722
Luke.

37:25.927 --> 37:27.838
DONNA: Where did you say you found him?

37:28.407 --> 37:30.796
What do you think
about the parade rehearsal?

37:31.927 --> 37:34.646
Don't do it.

37:36.247 --> 37:39.478
Call McDonald and tell her to cancel it.

37:39.807 --> 37:42.196
I've got a Mr. Jenkins on the line.

37:43.167 --> 37:45.397
