38:12.447 --> 38:14.756
Thomas County Sheriff, can I help you?

38:17.767 --> 38:19.883
No, we haven't found him. No.

38:55.687 --> 38:58.565
Sorry we're late.
We were just over seeing Everett.

38:58.927 --> 39:00.679
We're going over, too.

39:35.607 --> 39:37.086
- Donna?
- Yes?

39:37.567 --> 39:40.957
Wade. Look, I'm with Mr. Jenkins.

39:43.167 --> 39:45.044
Yeah, send an ambulance. Tell them...

39:45.647 --> 39:47.444
Tell them there's no rush.

39:48.247 --> 39:50.841
I'll probably be back in about an hour.

39:51.327 --> 39:53.045
WADE: Anything new?
DONNA: Nope.

39:53.487 --> 39:57.560
The roadblocks are set, the patrols are out,
and everything's quiet as can be.

40:09.847 --> 40:11.200
[Whistle blowing]

40:19.767 --> 40:22.156
