42:20.487 --> 42:23.399
Move up. Move them up. Come on.

42:25.287 --> 42:27.118
[Horses neighing]

42:28.887 --> 42:32.562
All right, hold onto them.
Hold onto them, everybody.

42:32.647 --> 42:35.081
Hold on, everybody, to your music!

42:35.167 --> 42:37.761
Turn away from it and protect your eyes!

42:38.167 --> 42:39.646
I can't see.

42:39.727 --> 42:42.400
