44:48.607 --> 44:51.883
Wait a minute, get in there! Come on!

44:54.487 --> 44:55.636
Hurry.

44:57.967 --> 44:59.605
Come on, over here.

45:10.167 --> 45:11.919
[Car engine revving]

45:12.647 --> 45:14.877
You're okay now, Debra, you're okay.

45:20.167 --> 45:21.361
Oh, God.

45:26.567 --> 45:28.444
