47:39.407 --> 47:42.524
You punk, psycho idiot, horse's ass!

47:55.927 --> 47:57.565
Hello, somebody, hello?

47:57.647 --> 47:59.877
DONNA: Yes, who is this?
MARGIE: This is Margie Johnson.

47:59.967 --> 48:02.162
