50:22.607 --> 50:24.199
He's slowing down.

50:27.367 --> 50:28.720
He's stopping.

50:31.167 --> 50:32.395
He's stopped.

50:39.007 --> 50:40.235
Shit!

50:42.487 --> 50:44.398
WADE: Ray? Talk to us!

50:44.527 --> 50:46.995
RAY: I missed him twice.
God damn it. I don't believe it.

50:47.087 --> 50:50.602
Where's Metcalf? Where's Denson?
Where's Mac Gruder? Where's Berry?

50:51.607 --> 50:53.916
Denson, Mac Gruder, Berry, Metcalf.

50:59.527 --> 51:00.880
