51:22.567 --> 51:25.001
Move. Everybody, move.

51:26.167 --> 51:27.839
- You got it.
- Right.

51:56.887 --> 51:58.684
DONNA: Whas happening out there, Ray?

51:58.767 --> 52:00.086
RAY: I'm moving as fast as I can.

52:00.167 --> 52:02.886
Christ, he's probably hit
the Mesa Road intersection by now.

52:02.967 --> 52:04.286
Christ knows where he's going.

52:04.367 --> 52:06.756
He's not gonna wait around for us,
you know?

52:06.847 --> 52:07.996
I see him.

52:08.087 --> 52:09.725
He's at the foot of the Mesa.

52:09.807 --> 52:13.197
METCALF: Ray, is Metcalf. We're coming in,
