52:13.287 --> 52:15.881
Got him. He's trapping himself up there.

52:16.887 --> 52:18.320
Come on, guys.

52:41.367 --> 52:44.757
Got him. We got him.
There's no way down but straight down.

52:46.327 --> 52:47.999
Ray, don't lose him.

52:48.167 --> 52:50.397
You boys better move
if you wanna join in on the fun.

52:50.487 --> 52:52.398
I'm getting near the top.

52:54.367 --> 52:55.561
Geez!

53:22.487 --> 53:23.636
Jesus.

53:27.687 --> 53:29.678
